{"s":"did:fide:0x30205c57a86dc723ff954eb875447ddcc028be16","sr":"https://github.com/fide/cli","p":"did:fide:0x3120a76e1bc34410d95d99c7e64955df44211b42","pr":"https://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment","o":"did:fide:0xa0a00e92a54a5f53f77d54210358cdd06f51b13e","or":"Keep help short and execution-focused so agents can find the next valid command without context bloat."}
{"s":"did:fide:0x30205c57a86dc723ff954eb875447ddcc028be16","sr":"https://github.com/fide/cli","p":"did:fide:0x3120a76e1bc34410d95d99c7e64955df44211b42","pr":"https://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment","o":"did:fide:0xa0a0aa8694167c19a13eb9abd9f6210453c24048","or":"Make commands explicit about domain and side effects so agents do not choose the wrong operation or mutate the wrong state."}
{"s":"did:fide:0x30205c57a86dc723ff954eb875447ddcc028be16","sr":"https://github.com/fide/cli","p":"did:fide:0x3120a76e1bc34410d95d99c7e64955df44211b42","pr":"https://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment","o":"did:fide:0xa0a0127868d62046d4c10b8b939b281f12bffaa8","or":"Separate authored local state from built runtime state so agents have one clear source of truth for authoring and a separate explicit step for publishing or querying derived state."}
{"s":"did:fide:0x30205c57a86dc723ff954eb875447ddcc028be16","sr":"https://github.com/fide/cli","p":"did:fide:0x3120a76e1bc34410d95d99c7e64955df44211b42","pr":"https://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment","o":"did:fide:0xa0a0d241ab48fdc42cf3774cd8728dfbd407fe45","or":"Prefer lazy setup over explicit init ceremony because extra setup commands create more failure points and workflow overhead."}
{"s":"did:fide:0x30205c57a86dc723ff954eb875447ddcc028be16","sr":"https://github.com/fide/cli","p":"did:fide:0x3120a76e1bc34410d95d99c7e64955df44211b42","pr":"https://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment","o":"did:fide:0xa0a01191cc77506e6b0c6f91752544d8b73e941f","or":"Keep command surfaces small and composable so agents can infer the right workflow with fewer planning mistakes."}
{"s":"did:fide:0x30205c57a86dc723ff954eb875447ddcc028be16","sr":"https://github.com/fide/cli","p":"did:fide:0x3120a76e1bc34410d95d99c7e64955df44211b42","pr":"https://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment","o":"did:fide:0xa0a0c0d513e8f0fa6a3d0b7dc079a61d095f3d9d","or":"Use domain-specific flags such as --store and --fide-dir instead of overloaded selectors such as --target."}
{"s":"did:fide:0x30205c57a86dc723ff954eb875447ddcc028be16","sr":"https://github.com/fide/cli","p":"did:fide:0x3120a76e1bc34410d95d99c7e64955df44211b42","pr":"https://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment","o":"did:fide:0xa0a0c1d4342920a1fcaafdcdc19e133c4b47973a","or":"Treat local files as reviewable source artifacts so humans and agents can inspect and diff authored state."}
{"s":"did:fide:0x30205c57a86dc723ff954eb875447ddcc028be16","sr":"https://github.com/fide/cli","p":"did:fide:0x3120a76e1bc34410d95d99c7e64955df44211b42","pr":"https://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment","o":"did:fide:0xa0a0c2cffbe69184240a1742c051f6d5f68ed3d8","or":"Make runtime operations explicit so agents can distinguish publishing state from querying state."}
